mpton]] | Filmed as ''[[Death Watch]]''. |- | Novel | ''Tiger! Tiger!''* | ''[[The Stars My Destination]]'' | [[Alfred Bester]] | |- | Novel | ''On Her Majesty's Wizardly Service'' | ''[[To Visit the Queen]]''* | [[Diane Duane]] | |- | Novel | ''Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Spy''* | ''Catch a Falling Spy'' | [[Len Deighton]] | |- | Novel | ''[[Where Rainbows End]]''* | ''Love, Rosie'', or ''Rosie Dunne'' | [[Cecelia Ahern]] | |- | Novel | ''[[Why Didn't They Ask Evans?]]''* | ''The Boomerang Clue'' | [[Agatha Christie]] | |- | Novel | ''Wilkins' Tooth''* | ''Witch's Business'' | [[Diana Wynne Jones]] | |}
